&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://flink.apache.org/&quot;&gt;Apache Flink(Ïù¥Ìïò Flink)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Îäî Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞ Ïä§Ìä∏Î¶¨Î∞ç Î∞è Î∞∞Ïπò Ï≤òÎ¶¨Ïö© Ïò§Ìîà ÏÜåÏä§ ÌîÑÎ†àÏûÑÏõåÌÅ¨ÏûÖÎãàÎã§. ÎπÑÏä∑ÌïòÍ≤å Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞ Ïä§Ìä∏Î¶¨Î∞çÏù¥ÎÇò Î∞∞Ïπò ÌîÑÎ°úÏÑ∏Ïã±ÏùÑ ÏúÑÌï¥ Kafka Streams, Spark, Kinesis Îì±Ïù¥ ÏûàÎäîÎç∞Ïöî, Flink Í≥µÏãù ÌôàÌéòÏù¥ÏßÄÏóê Îì§Ïñ¥Í∞ÄÎ©¥ Î®ºÏ†Ä CatchphraseÍ∞Ä ÎààÏóê Îì§Ïñ¥ÏòµÎãàÎã§. &lt;strong&gt;Stateful Computations over Data Streams&lt;/strong&gt;. Ïôú Ïù¥ Î¨∏Íµ¨Î•º Í∞ïÏ°∞ÌïòÍ≥† ÏûàÏùÑÍπåÏöî?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/images/2024/09/18/apache-flink.png&quot; alt=&quot;Apache Flink&quot; title=&quot;Apache Flink&quot; class=&quot;center-image&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ïä§Ìä∏Î¶º(Stream)&lt;/strong&gt;Ïù¥ÎûÄ &lt;strong&gt;ÌäπÏ†ï ÏãúÏ†êÏóê ÏùºÏñ¥ÎÇú Ïù¥Î≤§Ìä∏Ïùò Ïó∞ÏÜç&lt;/strong&gt;ÏùÑ ÏùòÎØ∏Ìï©ÎãàÎã§. ÏòàÎ•º Îì§Ïñ¥, Ïò®ÎèÑ, ÏäµÎèÑ Îì±Ïùò Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞Î•º Ïã§ÏãúÍ∞ÑÏúºÎ°ú ÏàòÏßëÌïòÎäî IoT ÎîîÎ∞îÏù¥Ïä§ÏóêÏÑúÎäî Î≥ÄÌôîÌïòÎäî Ïò®ÎèÑÏôÄ ÏäµÎèÑÍ∞Ä Ïä§Ìä∏Î¶ºÏúºÎ°ú Íµ¨ÏÑ±Îê† Ïàò ÏûàÏñ¥Ïöî. ÏÇ¨Ïö©ÏûêÍ∞Ä Ïï±ÏóêÏÑú ÌäπÏ†ï Î≤ÑÌäºÏùÑ ÌÅ¥Î¶≠ÌïúÎã§ÎçòÍ∞Ä ÌîºÎìúÏóêÏÑú Ïä§ÌÅ¨Î°§ÏùÑ ÌïòÎäî Îì±Ïùò ÌñâÎèô Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞Îì§ÎèÑ Ïä§Ìä∏Î¶ºÏúºÎ°ú Íµ¨ÏÑ±Îê† Ïàò ÏûàÏäµÎãàÎã§. Ïù¥Ï≤òÎüº Ïä§Ìä∏Î¶ºÏùÄ ÌäπÏ†ï ÏãúÏ†êÏóê ÏùºÏñ¥ÎÇòÎäî ÏûëÍ≥† ÎèÖÎ¶ΩÎêú Î≥ÄÌïòÏßÄ ÏïäÎäî Î∂àÎ≥Ä Í∞ùÏ≤¥ÏûÖÎãàÎã§. ÏûÖÎ†• Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞Í∞Ä Í≥†Ï†ïÎêú ÌÅ¨Í∏∞Ïùò Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞ ÏÖãÏúºÎ°ú Ï†úÍ≥µÎêòÎäî &lt;strong&gt;Î∞∞Ïπò Ï≤òÎ¶¨(Batch Processing)&lt;/strong&gt;ÏôÄ Îã§Î•¥Í≤å, Ïä§Ìä∏Î¶º Ï≤òÎ¶¨Îäî(Stream Processing)ÏùÄ ÏûÖÎ†• Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞Í∞Ä ÏßÄÏÜçÏ†ÅÏúºÎ°ú Î∞úÏÉùÌïòÍ≥† Ïù¥Í±∏ Ïã§ÏãúÍ∞ÑÏúºÎ°ú Ï≤òÎ¶¨ÌïòÎäîÍ≤å Î™©ÌëúÏòàÏöî. FlinkÎäî Îã®ÏàúÌûà ÏèüÏïÑÏßÄÎäî Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞Î•º Ï≤òÎ¶¨ÌïòÎäîÍ±∏ Î™©ÌëúÎ°ú ÌïòÏßÄ ÏïäÍ≥†, ÏÑ∏ÏÖò ÏúàÎèÑÏö∞(Session Window, ÌäπÏ†ï ÏãúÍ∞Ñ ÎèôÏïàÏùò ÏÇ¨Ïö©Ïûê ÌôúÎèô)ÎÇò ÏßëÍ≥Ñ(Aggregation, ÌèâÍ∑†, Ï¥ùÌï© Îì±) Îì± &lt;strong&gt;Î©îÎ™®Î¶¨ ÎÇ¥ÏóêÏÑú ÏÉÅÌÉúÎ•º Ïú†ÏßÄÌïòÍ≥† Í¥ÄÎ¶¨&lt;/strong&gt;Ìï† Ïàò ÏûàÎäî Í∞ïÎ†•Ìïú Í∏∞Îä•ÏùÑ Ï†úÍ≥µÌï©ÎãàÎã§. Ïõπ Ïï†ÌîåÎ¶¨ÏºÄÏù¥ÏÖòÏóêÏÑú ÏÇ¨Ïö©ÏûêÍ∞Ä Îã§ÏñëÌïú ÌéòÏù¥ÏßÄÎ•º Î∞©Î¨∏ÌïòÎäî ÎèôÏïà Í∞Å ÏÇ¨Ïö©ÏûêÏùò ÏÑ∏ÏÖòÏùÑ Ïã§ÏãúÍ∞ÑÏúºÎ°ú Ï∂îÏ†ÅÌïúÎã§ÎçòÍ∞Ä, Í≤∞Ï†ú ÏãúÏä§ÌÖúÏóêÏÑú Ïã§ÏãúÍ∞ÑÏúºÎ°ú Í±∞Îûò Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞Î•º Î™®ÎãàÌÑ∞ÎßÅÌïòÍ≥† ÌäπÏ†ï Ìå®ÌÑ¥ÏùÑ Ï∞æÏïÑ Ïù¥ÏÉÅ Í±∞ÎûòÎ•º ÌÉêÏßÄÌïòÎäî Îì± Ïã§ÏãúÍ∞ÑÏúºÎ°ú Î∞úÏÉùÌïòÎäî Ïä§Ìä∏Î¶º Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞ÏóêÏÑú ÏÉÅÌÉúÎ•º Ïú†ÏßÄÌïòÎ©¥ÏÑú Ïó∞ÏÇ∞ÏùÑ ÏàòÌñâÌï† Ïàò ÏûàÎäî Í∏∞Îä•ÏùÑ Ï†úÍ≥µÌï©ÎãàÎã§. Í∑∏Î¶¨Í≥† FlinkÏùò ÏÉÅÌÉú Í¥ÄÎ¶¨ Í∏∞Îä• ÎçïÎ∂ÑÏóê Ïï†ÌîåÎ¶¨ÏºÄÏù¥ÏÖò Í∞úÎ∞úÏûêÎäî Ïù¥ ÎèÑÍµ¨Î•º ÌôúÏö©Ìï¥ÏÑú Îã§ÏñëÌïú Ïã§ÏãúÍ∞Ñ Ïï†ÌîåÎ¶¨ÏºÄÏù¥ÏÖòÏùÑ Íµ¨Ï∂ïÌïòÍ≥† ÏâΩÍ≤å Ïö¥ÏòÅÌï† Ïàò ÏûàÍ≤å ÎêòÏóàÏäµÎãàÎã§.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;ÎèÑÍµ¨Î•º Ïûò Ïì∞Î†§Î©¥ Ïù¥ ÎèÑÍµ¨Í∞Ä Ïñ¥ÎñªÍ≤å ÎèåÏïÑÍ∞ÄÎäîÏßÄ, Í∑∏Î¶¨Í≥† Ïñ¥ÎîîÏóê Ïì∞Îäî Í≤ÉÏù¥Í≥† Ïñ¥ÎñªÍ≤å Ïì∞Îäî Í±¥ÏßÄ ÏïÑÎäîÍ≤å Ï§ëÏöîÌïòÍ∏∞ ÎïåÎ¨∏Ïóê &lt;a href=&quot;https://flink.apache.org/what-is-flink/flink-architecture/&quot;&gt;Architecture&lt;/a&gt;ÏôÄ &lt;a href=&quot;https://flink.apache.org/what-is-flink/flink-applications/&quot;&gt;API&lt;/a&gt;ÎèÑ Ï∞∏Í≥†ÌïòÏãúÎ©¥ Ï¢ãÍ≤†Ïñ¥Ïöî. Flink ÌïôÏäµÏùÑ ÏúÑÌï¥ Ïò®ÎùºÏù∏ Í∞ïÏùòÎèÑ Îì§Ïñ¥Î¥§ÎäîÎç∞ ÏïÑÏßÅÍπåÏßÄÎäî Í≥µÏãù Î¨∏ÏÑúÍ∞Ä ÏµúÍ≥†Îùº ÏÉùÍ∞ÅÌï¥Ïöî. Ïó¨Í∏∞ÏÑú Îî∞Î°ú ÏÑ§Î™ÖÏùÄ ÌïòÏßÄ ÏïäÍ≤†ÏäµÎãàÎã§.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/images/2024/09/18/flink-task-manager.png&quot; alt=&quot;Flink Task Manager&quot; title=&quot;Flink Task Manager&quot; class=&quot;center-image&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;center&gt;Flink Runtime Flow&lt;/center&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;advantages&quot;&gt;Advantages&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Ï†úÍ∞Ä ÏÑúÎ≤Ñ Í∞úÎ∞úÏûêÎãà.. Í∞úÎ∞úÏûê Í¥ÄÏ†êÏóêÏÑú FlinkÏùò Í∞ÄÏû• ÎåÄÌëúÏ†ÅÏù∏ ÌäπÏßïÏùÑ ÍºΩÏúºÎùºÎ©¥ &lt;strong&gt;Standalone&lt;/strong&gt;Í≥º &lt;strong&gt;Checkpoints&lt;/strong&gt;Î•º Ïù¥ÏïºÍ∏∞ÌïòÍ≥† Ïã∂ÏäµÎãàÎã§. ÏùºÎ°ÄÎ°ú Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞ Ïä§Ìä∏Î¶¨Î∞çÏóê ÎßéÏù¥ ÌôúÏö©ÎêòÎäî &lt;a href=&quot;https://kafka.apache.org/documentation/streams/&quot;&gt;Apache Kafka Streams&lt;/a&gt;ÏùÄ Ïï†ÌîåÎ¶¨ÏºÄÏù¥ÏÖòÏùò ÏùºÎ∂ÄÎ°ú Ïã§ÌñâÎêòÎäî ÎùºÏù¥Î∏åÎü¨Î¶¨Ïù∏ Î∞òÎ©¥, FlinkÎäî ÏûêÏ≤¥ Ïä§Ìä∏Î¶º Ï≤òÎ¶¨ ÏóîÏßÑÏùÑ Í∞ÄÏßÄÍ≥† ÏûàÎäî ÌîÑÎ†àÏûÑÏõåÌÅ¨ÎùºÏÑú ÎèÖÎ¶ΩÏ†ÅÏúºÎ°ú Î∞∞Ìè¨ÏôÄ Ïã§ÌñâÏù¥ Í∞ÄÎä•Ìï©ÎãàÎã§. IDEAÏóêÏÑú ÏΩîÎìúÎßå ÏûëÏÑ±Ìï¥ÏÑú Ïã§ÌñâÌïòÎ©¥ ÎÇ¥Ïû•Îêú Mini ClusterÎ•º Í∏∞Î∞òÏúºÎ°ú ÏâΩÍ≤å ÎîîÎ≤ÑÍπÖÍπåÏßÄ Ìï† Ïàò ÏûàÏäµÎãàÎã§. Í∑∏Î¶¨Í≥† Ï≤¥ÌÅ¨Ìè¨Ïù∏Ìä∏(Checkpoints)Î•º ÌÜµÌï¥ Ïï†ÌîåÎ¶¨ÏºÄÏù¥ÏÖòÏùò ÏÉÅÌÉúÎ•º Ï£ºÍ∏∞Ï†ÅÏúºÎ°ú Ï†ÄÏû•ÌïòÏó¨ Ïû•Ïï† Î∞úÏÉùÏãú ÏûêÎèôÏúºÎ°ú Î≥µÍµ¨Ìï¥Ï§çÎãàÎã§(Fault-tolerance). Ï†ïÌôïÌûà Ìïú Î≤àÎßå(Exactly-Once) Ï≤òÎ¶¨ÌïúÎã§ÎçòÍ∞Ä Two-Phase Commit Í∏∞Î∞òÏùò ÏõêÏûêÏ†Å Ïª§Î∞ãÏùÑ ÌÜµÌï¥ Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞ ÏùºÍ¥ÄÏÑ±ÏùÑ Î≥¥Ïû•Ìï† ÏàòÎèÑ ÏûàÏäµÎãàÎã§.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Í∑∏Î¶¨Í≥† ÌïòÎÇòÎßå Îçî ÍºΩÏúºÎùºÎ©¥ Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞ ÌîÑÎ°úÏÑ∏Ïã±ÏùÑ ÏúÑÌïú Í≥†ÏàòÏ§ÄÏùò APIÏóê ÎåÄÌï¥ÏÑú Ïù¥ÏïºÍ∏∞ÌïòÍ≥† Ïã∂Ïñ¥Ïöî. &lt;a href=&quot;https://spark.apache.org/docs/latest/rdd-programming-guide.html&quot;&gt;Spark RDD&lt;/a&gt;Î•º Îã§Î§Ñ Î≥¥Ïã† Î∂ÑÎì§Ïù¥ÎùºÎ©¥ ÏïÑÏ£º ÏâΩÍ≤å ÏÇ¨Ïö©Ìï¥Î≥º Ïàò ÏûàÏùÑÍ±∞Îùº ÏÉùÍ∞ÅÌï¥Ïöî.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/images/2024/09/18/spark-flink-operator.png&quot; alt=&quot;Flink Task Manager&quot; title=&quot;Flink Task Manager&quot; class=&quot;center-image&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Ïù¥ OperatorÎì§ÏùÄ Spark RDDÎ•º Î™®Î•¥ÎçîÎùºÎèÑ JavaÎÇò KotlinÏùÑ ÏÇ¨Ïö©ÌïòÍ±∞ÎÇò Ìï®ÏàòÌòï ÌîÑÎ°úÍ∑∏ÎûòÎ∞çÏùò Í≥†Ï∞® Ìï®Ïàò(Higher-order Functions)Ïóê ÏùµÏàôÌïú Î∂ÑÎì§Ïù¥ÎùºÎ©¥ ÏâΩÍ≤å Ï†ëÍ∑ºÌï† Ïàò ÏûàÏùÑÍ±∞Îùº ÏÉùÍ∞ÅÌï©ÎãàÎã§. Ïâ¥ ÏÉà ÏóÜÏù¥ Îì§Ïñ¥Ïò§Îäî Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞ Ïä§Ìä∏Î¶ºÏùÑ Îã§Î•∏ ÌòïÌÉúÎ°ú Î≥ÄÌôòÌïòÍ≥† Ïã∂ÏùÑÎïåÏóêÎäî &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;map&lt;/code&gt;Í≥º Í∞ôÏùÄ Ìï®ÏàòÎ•º Ïù¥Ïö©Ìï¥ÏÑú ÏÉàÎ°úÏö¥ Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞ Ïä§Ìä∏Î¶ºÏúºÎ°ú Î≥ÄÌôòÌïòÍ≥†, ÌäπÏ†ï Ï°∞Í±¥Ïóê ÎßåÏ°±ÌïòÎäî Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞Îßå ÌïÑÌÑ∞ÎßÅÌïòÍ≥† Ïã∂Îã§Î©¥ &lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;filter&lt;/code&gt; Ìï®ÏàòÎ•º ÏÇ¨Ïö©ÌïòÎ©¥ Îê©ÎãàÎã§.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;language-kotlin highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;// ÏûÖÎ†• Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞ Ïä§Ìä∏Î¶º ÏÉùÏÑ±&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;kd&quot;&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;py&quot;&gt;input&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nc&quot;&gt;DataStream&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nc&quot;&gt;Int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;env&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nf&quot;&gt;fromElements&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;// Filter: ÏßùÏàòÏù∏ ÏöîÏÜåÎßå ÌïÑÌÑ∞ÎßÅ&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;kd&quot;&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;py&quot;&gt;filtered&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nc&quot;&gt;DataStream&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nc&quot;&gt;Int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;input&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nf&quot;&gt;filter&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;kd&quot;&gt;object&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;err&quot;&gt;: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nc&quot;&gt;FilterFunction&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nc&quot;&gt;Int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;override&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;fun&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nf&quot;&gt;filter&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;value&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nc&quot;&gt;Int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;):&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nc&quot;&gt;Boolean&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;value&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;%&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;==&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;})&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;c1&quot;&gt;// Map: ÌïÑÌÑ∞ÎßÅÎêú ÏöîÏÜåÎ•º Î¨∏ÏûêÏó¥Î°ú Î≥ÄÌôò&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;kd&quot;&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;py&quot;&gt;stringified&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nc&quot;&gt;DataStream&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nc&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;filtered&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nf&quot;&gt;map&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;kd&quot;&gt;object&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;err&quot;&gt;: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nc&quot;&gt;MapFunction&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nc&quot;&gt;Int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nc&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;override&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;fun&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nf&quot;&gt;map&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;value&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nc&quot;&gt;Int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;):&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nc&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;value&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nf&quot;&gt;toString&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;()&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;})&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;use-cases&quot;&gt;Use Cases&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nightlies.apache.org/flink/flink-docs-stable/&quot;&gt;Apache Flink Documentation&lt;/a&gt;ÏùÑ ÏÇ¥Ìé¥Î≥¥Î©¥ SourceÏôÄ SinkÎùºÎäî Ïö©Ïñ¥Í∞Ä ÎßéÏù¥ Î≥¥Ïù¥ÎäîÎç∞, Apache Flink ÎøêÎßå ÏïÑÎãàÎùº Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞ ÏóîÏßÄÎãàÏñ¥ÎßÅÏóêÏÑú ÌùîÌûà ÏÇ¨Ïö©ÎêòÎäî Ïö©Ïñ¥ÏûÖÎãàÎã§. &lt;strong&gt;SourceÎäî Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞ ÌååÏù¥ÌîÑÎùºÏù∏Ïùò ÏãúÏûë ÏßÄÏ†ê&lt;/strong&gt;ÏúºÎ°ú, Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞Î•º ÏàòÏßëÌïòÏó¨ ÏãúÏä§ÌÖúÏóê ÏûÖÎ†•ÌïòÎäî Ïó≠Ìï†ÏùÑ Ìï©ÎãàÎã§. &lt;strong&gt;SinkÎäî Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞ ÌååÏù¥ÌîÑÎùºÏù∏Ïùò Ï¢ÖÎ£å ÏßÄÏ†ê&lt;/strong&gt;ÏúºÎ°ú, Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞Î•º Ïô∏Î∂Ä ÏãúÏä§ÌÖúÏúºÎ°ú Ï∂úÎ†•ÌïòÏó¨ Ï†ÄÏû•ÌïòÍ±∞ÎÇò Ï†ÑÏÜ°ÌïòÎäî Ïó≠Ìï†ÏùÑ Ìï©ÎãàÎã§. Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞ ÏÜåÏä§(Source)ÏôÄ Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞ Ïã±ÌÅ¨(Sink)Î°úÏÑú Ïô∏Î∂Ä ÏãúÏä§ÌÖúÍ≥º Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞Î•º Ï£ºÍ≥† Î∞õÏùÑ Ïàò ÏûàÎèÑÎ°ù Ïó¨Îü¨ ConnectorÎ•º Ï†úÍ≥µÌïòÍ≥† ÏûàÏñ¥Ïöî. ÌòÑÏû¨(2024.09.18) Í∏∞Ï§ÄÏúºÎ°ú ÏïÑÎûòÏôÄ Í∞ôÏùÄ Source, Sink ConnectorÎ•º Ï†úÍ≥µÌïòÍ≥† ÏûàÏäµÎãàÎã§. Ïù¥ ÎÇ¥Ïö©ÏùÄ &lt;a href=&quot;https://nightlies.apache.org/flink/flink-docs-master/docs/connectors/datastream/overview/#flink-project-connectors&quot;&gt;Flink Project Connectors&lt;/a&gt;ÏóêÏÑú ÌôïÏù∏Ìï† Ïàò ÏûàÏñ¥Ïöî.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nightlies.apache.org/flink/flink-docs-master/docs/connectors/datastream/kafka/&quot;&gt;Apache Kafka&lt;/a&gt;¬†(source/sink)&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nightlies.apache.org/flink/flink-docs-master/docs/connectors/datastream/dynamodb/&quot;&gt;Amazon DynamoDB&lt;/a&gt;¬†(sink)&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nightlies.apache.org/flink/flink-docs-master/docs/connectors/datastream/kinesis/&quot;&gt;Amazon Kinesis Data Streams&lt;/a&gt;¬†(source/sink)&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nightlies.apache.org/flink/flink-docs-master/docs/connectors/datastream/elasticsearch/&quot;&gt;Elasticsearch&lt;/a&gt;¬†(sink)&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nightlies.apache.org/flink/flink-docs-master/docs/connectors/datastream/opensearch/&quot;&gt;Opensearch&lt;/a&gt;¬†(sink)&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nightlies.apache.org/flink/flink-docs-master/docs/connectors/datastream/filesystem/&quot;&gt;FileSystem&lt;/a&gt;¬†(source/sink)&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nightlies.apache.org/flink/flink-docs-master/docs/connectors/datastream/jdbc/&quot;&gt;JDBC&lt;/a&gt;¬†(sink)&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nightlies.apache.org/flink/flink-docs-master/docs/connectors/datastream/mongodb/&quot;&gt;MongoDB&lt;/a&gt;¬†(source/sink)&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://bahir.apache.org/docs/flink/current/flink-streaming-redis/&quot;&gt;Redis&lt;/a&gt;¬†(sink)&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://bahir.apache.org/docs/flink/current/flink-streaming-netty/&quot;&gt;Netty&lt;/a&gt;¬†(source)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞ ÏÜåÏä§(source)ÏóêÏÑú Ïã§ÏãúÍ∞ÑÏúºÎ°ú Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞Î•º ÏùΩÏñ¥ÏÑú, ÏÉàÎ°úÏö¥ ÌòïÌÉúÎ°ú Î≥ÄÌôòÌïòÍ±∞ÎÇò Î°úÏª¨ Ïä§ÌÜ†Î¶¨ÏßÄÏóê Ï†ÄÏû•Ìï¥ÎÜìÍ≥† SQL ÏøºÎ¶¨Î•º ÌÜµÌï¥ Ïú†ÏùòÎØ∏Ìïú Í≤∞Í≥ºÎ•º ÎßåÎì§Í≥†, Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞ Ïã±ÌÅ¨(sink)Ïóê Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞Î•º Ï∂úÎ†•&lt;/strong&gt;Ìï©ÎãàÎã§. Ïù¥Îü∞ Í∏∞Îä•Ïù¥ ÏûàÎã§Î©¥ Ïö∞Î¶¨Îäî Ïñ¥Îñ§ Î¨∏Ï†úÎ•º Ìö®Í≥ºÏ†ÅÏúºÎ°ú Ìï¥Í≤∞Ìï† Ïàò ÏûàÏùÑÍπåÏöî? &lt;a href=&quot;https://flink.apache.org/what-is-flink/use-cases/&quot;&gt;Í≥µÏãù Î¨∏ÏÑúÏùò ÎåÄÌëúÏ†ÅÏù∏ Ïú†Ïä§ÏºÄÏù¥Ïä§&lt;/a&gt;ÏóêÏÑúÎäî Ïù¥Î≤§Ìä∏ ÎìúÎ¶¨Î∏ê Ïï†ÌîåÎ¶¨ÏºÄÏù¥ÏÖò Í∞úÎ∞úÍ≥º Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞ Î∂ÑÏÑù Í∑∏Î¶¨Í≥† Îç∞Ïù¥ÌÑ∞ ÌååÏù¥ÌîÑÎùºÏù∏Ïóê Íµ¨Ï∂ïÏùò Í∏∞Î∞òÏùÑ Îã§ÏßÄÎäîÎç∞ ÏÇ¨Ïö©Îê† Ïàò ÏûàÎã§Í≥† ÎßêÌïòÍ≥† ÏûàÏäµÎãàÎã§.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/images/2024/09/18/flink-usecases-eventdrivenapps.png&quot; alt=&quot;Event-driven Applications&quot; title=&quot;Event-driven Applications&quot; class=&quot;center-image&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;center&gt;Flink support event-driven applications&lt;/center&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/images/2024/09/18/flink-usecases-analytics.png&quot; alt=&quot;Data Analytics Applications&quot; title=&quot;Data Analytics Applications&quot; class=&quot;center-image&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

